            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pot with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Add your <strong>tomato paste</strong> with your <strong>ground coriander</strong> and <strong>remaining ground smoked paprika </strong>and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
