    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your<strong> chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>roasted garlic paste</strong> and <strong>beef stock mix </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
