    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 700ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[1.1L] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[1.3L]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>with your <strong>fine egg noodles </strong>and <strong>drained sweetcorn</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 1-2 min or until the noodles are tender – this is your <strong>corn</strong> <strong>birria-inspired ramen</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
