    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> corn</strong> <strong>birria-inspired ramen</strong> topped<strong> </strong>with the <strong>crispy pork</strong>,<strong> grated cheddar </strong>and<strong> sliced spring onion </strong>– this is your <strong>crispy pork & corn birria-inspired ramen</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
